  "title": "Assistant Housekeeper/ Supervisor / Orchard (Monday - Friday)",
  "description": "<p>Monday - Friday</p><p>Location: Orchard Central</p><p>Working Hours: 9 AM - 6 PM / 10 AM - 8:30 PM</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Set housekeeping work standards and procedures</li><li>Supervise, train, and guide housekeeping team members</li><li>Conduct training and demonstrate equipment use and procedures</li><li>Inspect apartments for cleanliness and maintenance; arrange periodic cleaning</li><li>Follow up on maintenance issues and special attention for VIP apartments</li><li>Update Front Office on room readiness</li><li>Investigate and resolve housekeeping complaints; recommend improvements</li><li>Participate in hiring, performance management, and team meetings</li><li>Prevent misuse of linen/equipment and report damages</li><li>Perform cleaning if required (staff shortage/emergency)</li><li>Attend meetings and support company policies and values</li></ul><p><strong>Other Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Uphold company mission, vision, and policies</li><li>Act as a role model demonstrate professionalism, innovation, and people management</li><li>Ensure effective daily communication and internal coordination</li><li>Support HR activities (contract coordination, discipline, best practices)</li><li>Participate in community events and maintain strict confidentiality and professionalism</li><li>Take on special projects as assigned</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please WhatsApp me at 8779 6100 or send in your resume to willie.goh@swiftsearchglobal.com</p><p><br /></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Willie Goh | EA Reg No: R2197853</p><p><br /></p><p>Swift Search Global Pte Ltd | EA No: 18C9495</p><p><br /></p>",
